### GuideNote API Tests

### 1. Get My Notes (GET)
GET https://localhost:7012/api/GuideNote/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Upload Attachment (POST)
POST https://localhost:7012/api/GuideNote/upload-attachment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 3. Create Note with Attachments (POST)
POST https://localhost:7012/api/GuideNote/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": 1,
  "title": "Test Note with Attachments",
  "content": "This is a test note content with image attachments",
  "attachmentUrls": [
    "/uploads/guidenotes/abc123.jpg",
    "/uploads/guidenotes/def456.png"
  ]
}

### 4. Update Note (PUT)
PUT https://localhost:7012/api/GuideNote/notes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Test Note",
  "content": "This is an updated test note content",
  "mediaUrls": []
}

### 5. Delete Note (DELETE)
DELETE https://localhost:7012/api/GuideNote/notes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get My Bookings (GET)
GET https://localhost:7012/api/GuideNote/my-bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. TourOperator Get All Notes (GET)
GET https://localhost:7012/api/GuideNote/tour-operator/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{tour_operator_token}}

### 8. TourOperator Update Extra Cost (PUT)
PUT https://localhost:7012/api/GuideNote/notes/1/extra-cost
Authorization: Bearer {{tour_operator_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "extraCost": 50.00
} 